244
00:18:50,189 --> 00:18:54,182
- How do you know it was him?
- I'd believe anything of him.

245
00:18:54,349 --> 00:18:56,909
I thought I liked him once.
Now I know the gentleman.

246
00:18:58,949 --> 00:19:01,622
